OBJECT Report 78700 Purchase Order INFRA DK.SE
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=NAVW17.10.00.36078,4PS7.00,RISA;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    Permissions=TableData 17=r,
                TableData 38=rm;
    CaptionML=ENU=Order;
    OnInitReport=BEGIN
                   GLSetup.GET;
                   PurchSetup.GET;
                 END;

    PreviewMode=PrintLayout;
  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 4458;    ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table38;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Document Type,No.)
                                 WHERE(Document Type=CONST(Order));
               ReqFilterHeadingML=ENU=Purchase Order;
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               //*4PS.sn
                               IF (NOT CurrReport.PREVIEW) AND (DirectPostOrder = DirectPostOrder::"According to Vendor") THEN
                                 DirectPosting;

                               DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));
                               //*4PS.en
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  LrecPOLine@1000 : Record 39;
                                  LrecAdvice@1001 : Record 11012055;
                                  LrecUserSetup@1004 : Record 91;
                                  LrecEmployee@1005 : Record 5200;
                                  LcodCreatedBy@1003 : Code[20];
                                  LcodTempProj@1007 : Code[20];
                                  LintLineCount@1002 : Integer;
                                  i@1006 : Integer;
                                BEGIN
                                  CurrReport.LANGUAGE := Language.GetLanguageID("Language Code");
                                  HeaderText := Text004;

                                  CheckPhase; //**4PS.n

                                  CompanyInfo.GET;
                                  //>> RISA
                                  CompanyInfo.CALCFIELDS(Picture);
                                  CLEAR(GrecCountryRegion);
                                  IF NOT GrecCountryRegion.GET(CompanyInfo."Country/Region Code") THEN;
                                  //<< RISA

                                  IF RespCenter.GET("Responsibility Center") THEN BEGIN
                                    FormatAddr.RespCenter(CompanyAddr,RespCenter);
                                    CompanyInfo."Phone No." := RespCenter."Phone No.";
                                    CompanyInfo."Fax No." := RespCenter."Fax No.";
                                  END ELSE
                                    FormatAddr.Company(CompanyAddr,CompanyInfo);

                                  CheckDimensionAddress("Shortcut Dimension 1 Code"); //**4PS.n

                                  DimSetEntry1.SETRANGE("Dimension Set ID","Dimension Set ID");

                                  IF "Purchaser Code" = '' THEN BEGIN
                                    SalesPurchPerson.INIT;
                                    PurchaserText := '';
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    SalesPurchPerson.GET("Purchaser Code");
                                    PurchaserText := Text000
                                  END;
                                  IF "Your Reference" = '' THEN
                                    ReferenceText := ''
                                  ELSE
                                    ReferenceText := FIELDCAPTION("Your Reference");
                                  IF "VAT Registration No." = '' THEN
                                    VATNoText := ''
                                  ELSE
                                    VATNoText := FIELDCAPTION("VAT Registration No.");
                                  IF "Currency Code" = '' THEN BEGIN
                                    GLSetup.TESTFIELD("LCY Code");
                                    TotalText := STRSUBSTNO(Text001,GLSetup."LCY Code");
                                    TotalInclVATText := STRSUBSTNO(Text002,GLSetup."LCY Code");
                                    TotalExclVATText := STRSUBSTNO(Text006,GLSetup."LCY Code");
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    TotalText := STRSUBSTNO(Text001,"Currency Code");
                                    TotalInclVATText := STRSUBSTNO(Text002,"Currency Code");
                                    TotalExclVATText := STRSUBSTNO(Text006,"Currency Code");
                                  END;

                                  FormatAddr.PurchHeaderBuyFrom(BuyFromAddr,"Purchase Header");
                                  IF "Buy-from Vendor No." <> "Pay-to Vendor No." THEN
                                    FormatAddr.PurchHeaderPayTo(VendAddr,"Purchase Header");
                                  IF "Payment Terms Code" = '' THEN
                                    PaymentTerms.INIT
                                  ELSE BEGIN
                                    PaymentTerms.GET("Payment Terms Code");
                                    PaymentTerms.TranslateDescription(PaymentTerms,"Language Code");
                                  END;
                                  IF "Prepmt. Payment Terms Code" = '' THEN
                                    PrepmtPaymentTerms.INIT
                                  ELSE BEGIN
                                    PrepmtPaymentTerms.GET("Prepmt. Payment Terms Code");
                                    PrepmtPaymentTerms.TranslateDescription(PrepmtPaymentTerms,"Language Code");
                                  END;
                                  IF "Shipment Method Code" = '' THEN
                                    ShipmentMethod.INIT
                                  ELSE BEGIN
                                    ShipmentMethod.GET("Shipment Method Code");
                                    ShipmentMethod.TranslateDescription(ShipmentMethod,"Language Code");
                                  END;

                                  FormatAddr.PurchHeaderShipTo(ShipToAddr,"Purchase Header");

                                  IF NOT CurrReport.PREVIEW THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ArchiveDocument THEN
                                      ArchiveManagement.StorePurchDocument("Purchase Header",LogInteraction);

                                    IF LogInteraction THEN BEGIN
                                      CALCFIELDS("No. of Archived Versions");
                                      SegManagement.LogDocument(
                                        13,"No.","Doc. No. Occurrence","No. of Archived Versions",DATABASE::Vendor,"Buy-from Vendor No.",
                                        "Purchaser Code",'',"Posting Description",'');
                                    END;
                                  END;
                                  PricesInclVATtxt := FORMAT("Prices Including VAT");

                                  //**4PS.sn
                                  FillJobInfo;

                                  { //DP00241.sn (24683)
                                  //Note:Example, not used/printed in this report. Can be used in customization.
                                  PlantOrderNo := GetPurchOrderPlantOrderNo("No."); //DP00241.n (24683)
                                  } //DP00241.en (24683)
                                  //**4PS.en

                                  //>> RISA
                                  CLEAR(GtxtCreatedByName);
                                  LrecPOLine.RESET;
                                  LrecPOLine.SETCURRENTKEY("Document Type","Purchase Route Reference");
                                  LrecPOLine.SETRANGE("Document Type","Document Type");
                                  LrecPOLine.SETRANGE("Document No.","No.");
                                  LrecPOLine.SETFILTER("Purchase Route Reference",'<>%1','');
                                  IF NOT LrecPOLine.ISEMPTY THEN BEGIN
                                    IF LrecPOLine.FINDSET(FALSE,FALSE) THEN BEGIN
                                      REPEAT
                                        //Advice Order
                                        LrecAdvice.RESET;
                                        LrecAdvice.SETCURRENTKEY("Purchase Route Reference");
                                        LrecAdvice.SETRANGE("Purchase Route Reference",LrecPOLine."Purchase Route Reference");
                                        IF LrecAdvice.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                          IF LcodCreatedBy = '' THEN
                                            LcodCreatedBy := LrecAdvice."Created by";
                                          IF LcodCreatedBy <> LrecAdvice."Created by" THEN BEGIN
                                            CLEAR(LcodCreatedBy);
                                            LintLineCount := 2;
                                          END;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (LrecPOLine.NEXT = 0) OR (LintLineCount = 2);
                                      IF LrecUserSetup.GET(LcodCreatedBy) THEN BEGIN
                                        IF LrecEmployee.GET(LrecUserSetup."Employee No.") THEN BEGIN
                                          LrecEmployee.CALCFIELDS("Full Name");
                                          GtxtCreatedByName := LrecEmployee."Full Name";
                                          IF LrecEmployee."Mobile Phone No." <> '' THEN
                                            GtxtCreatedByName += ' (Tel:' + LrecEmployee."Mobile Phone No." + ')';
                                        END;
                                      END;
                                    END;
                                  END;

                                  IF GtxtCreatedByName = '' THEN BEGIN
                                    GtxtCreatedByName := SalesPurchPerson.Name;
                                    IF SalesPurchPerson."Mobile Phone No." <> '' THEN
                                        GtxtCreatedByName += ' (Tel:' + SalesPurchPerson."Mobile Phone No." + ')';
                                  END;

                                  GtxtOrderNo := "No.";
                                  CLEAR(LintLineCount);
                                  CLEAR(LcodTempProj);
                                  LrecPOLine.SETRANGE("Document Type","Document Type");
                                  LrecPOLine.SETRANGE("Document No.","No.");
                                  LrecPOLine.SETFILTER("Job No.",'<>%1','');
                                  IF NOT LrecPOLine.ISEMPTY THEN BEGIN
                                    IF LrecPOLine.FINDSET(FALSE,FALSE) THEN BEGIN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF LrecPOLine."Job No." <> LcodTempProj THEN BEGIN
                                          LcodTempProj := LrecPOLine."Job No.";
                                          LintLineCount += 1;
                                        END;
                                      UNTIL (LrecPOLine.NEXT = 0) OR (LintLineCount > 1);
                                    END;
                                  END;

                                  IF LintLineCount = 1 THEN
                                      GtxtOrderNo += ' / ' + LrecPOLine."Job No.";

                                  FOR i := 1 TO 4 DO BEGIN
                                    GtxtPurchaseHeader[i] := LfncGetTextLines(i,"Language Code",0);
                                    GtxtPurchaseFooter[i] := LfncGetTextLines(i,"Language Code",1);
                                    GtxtPurchaseFootNote[i] := LfncGetTextLines(i,"Language Code",2);
                                  END;
                                  //<< RISA
                                END;

               OnPostDataItem=BEGIN
                                CheckPrintBlanketScheme; //**4PS.n
                              END;

               ReqFilterFields=No.,Buy-from Vendor No.,No. Printed }

    { 245 ;1   ;Column  ;DocType_PurchHeader ;
               SourceExpr="Document Type" }

    { 246 ;1   ;Column  ;No_PurchHeader      ;
               SourceExpr=GtxtOrderNo }

    { 45  ;1   ;Column  ;AmountCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=AmountCaptionLbl }

    { 78  ;1   ;Column  ;PurchLineInvDiscAmtCaption;
               SourceExpr=PurchLineInvDiscAmtCaptionLbl }

    { 105 ;1   ;Column  ;SubtotalCaption     ;
               SourceExpr=SubtotalCaptionLbl }

    { 86  ;1   ;Column  ;VATAmtLineVATCaption;
               SourceExpr=VATAmtLineVATCaptionLbl }

    { 88  ;1   ;Column  ;VATAmtLineVATAmtCaption;
               SourceExpr=VATAmtLineVATAmtCaptionLbl }

    { 31  ;1   ;Column  ;VATAmtSpecCaption   ;
               SourceExpr=VATAmtSpecCaptionLbl }

    { 130 ;1   ;Column  ;VATIdentifierCaption;
               SourceExpr=VATIdentifierCaptionLbl }

    { 134 ;1   ;Column  ;VATAmtLineInvDiscBaseAmtCaption;

               SourceExpr=HomePageCaptionLbl }

               SourceExpr=EmailIDCaptionLbl }

    { 16  ;1   ;Column  ;AllowInvoiceDiscCaption;
               SourceExpr=AllowInvoiceDiscCaptionLbl }

    { 1100525003;1;Column;PrintTextBln       ;
               SourceExpr=PrintTextBln }

    { 119 ;1   ;Column  ;TransportCaption    ;
               SourceExpr=TransportCaptionLbl }

    { 5701;1   ;DataItem;CopyLoop            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               NoOfLoops := ABS(NoOfCopies) + 1;
                               CopyText := '';
                               SETRANGE(Number,1,NoOfLoops);
                               OutputNo := 0;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  PrepmtPurchLine@1000 : TEMPORARY Record 39;
                                  TempPurchLine@1002 : TEMPORARY Record 39;
                                BEGIN
                                  CLEAR(PurchLine);
                                  CLEAR(PurchPost);
                                  PurchLine.DELETEALL;
                                  VATAmountLine.DELETEALL;
                                  PurchPost.GetPurchLines("Purchase Header",PurchLine,0);
                                  PurchLine.CalcVATAmountLines(0,"Purchase Header",PurchLine,VATAmountLine);
                                  PurchLine.UpdateVATOnLines(0,"Purchase Header",PurchLine,VATAmountLine);
                                  VATAmount := VATAmountLine.GetTotalVATAmount;
                                  VATBaseAmount := VATAmountLine.GetTotalVATBase;
                                  VATDiscountAmount :=
                                    VATAmountLine.GetTotalVATDiscount("Purchase Header"."Currency Code","Purchase Header"."Prices Including VAT");
                                  TotalAmountInclVAT := VATAmountLine.GetTotalAmountInclVAT;

                                  PrepmtInvBuf.DELETEALL;
                                  PurchPostPrepmt.GetPurchLines("Purchase Header",0,PrepmtPurchLine);
                                  IF NOT PrepmtPurchLine.ISEMPTY THEN BEGIN
                                    PurchPostPrepmt.GetPurchLinesToDeduct("Purchase Header",TempPurchLine);
                                    IF NOT TempPurchLine.ISEMPTY THEN
                                      PurchPostPrepmt.CalcVATAmountLines("Purchase Header",TempPurchLine,PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct,1);
                                  END;
                                  PurchPostPrepmt.CalcVATAmountLines("Purchase Header",PrepmtPurchLine,PrepmtVATAmountLine,0);
                                  IF PrepmtVATAmountLine.FINDSET THEN
                                    REPEAT
                                      PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct := PrepmtVATAmountLine;
                                      IF PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct.FIND THEN BEGIN
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."VAT Base" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."VAT Base" - PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."VAT Base";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."VAT Amount" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."VAT Amount" - PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."VAT Amount";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."Amount Including VAT" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."Amount Including VAT" -
                                          PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."Amount Including VAT";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."Line Amount" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."Line Amount" - PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."Line Amount";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."Inv. Disc. Base Amount" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."Inv. Disc. Base Amount" -
                                          PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."Inv. Disc. Base Amount";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."Invoice Discount Amount" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."Invoice Discount Amount" -
                                          PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."Invoice Discount Amount";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine."Calculated VAT Amount" := PrepmtVATAmountLine."Calculated VAT Amount" -
                                          PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct."Calculated VAT Amount";
                                        PrepmtVATAmountLine.MODIFY;
                                      END;
                                    UNTIL PrepmtVATAmountLine.NEXT = 0;
                                  PurchPostPrepmt.UpdateVATOnLines("Purchase Header",PrepmtPurchLine,PrepmtVATAmountLine,0);
                                  PurchPostPrepmt.BuildInvLineBuffer2("Purchase Header",PrepmtPurchLine,0,PrepmtInvBuf);
                                  PrepmtVATAmount := PrepmtVATAmountLine.GetTotalVATAmount;
                                  PrepmtVATBaseAmount := PrepmtVATAmountLine.GetTotalVATBase;
                                  PrepmtTotalAmountInclVAT := PrepmtVATAmountLine.GetTotalAmountInclVAT;

                                  IF Number > 1 THEN
                                    CopyText := Text003;
                                  CurrReport.PAGENO := 1;
                                  OutputNo := OutputNo + 1;

                                  TotalSubTotal := 0;
                                  TotalAmount := 0;
                                END;

               OnPostDataItem=BEGIN
                                IF NOT CurrReport.PREVIEW THEN
                                BEGIN //**4PS.n
                                  PurchCountPrinted.RUN("Purchase Header");
                                //**4PS.sn
                                  CASE ChangeStatus OF
                                    ChangeStatus::Released:
                                      ReleasePurchaseDocument.RUN("Purchase Header");
                                    ChangeStatus::Closed:
                                      ReleasePurchaseDocument.Close("Purchase Header");
                                  END;
                                END;
                                //**4PS.en
                              END;
                               }

    { 6455;2   ;DataItem;PageLoop            ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1)) }

    { 7574;3   ;DataItem;DimensionLoop1      ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1..));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF NOT ShowInternalInfo THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                    IF NOT DimSetEntry1.FINDSET THEN
                                      CurrReport.BREAK;
                                  END ELSE
                                    IF NOT Continue THEN
                                      CurrReport.BREAK;

                                  CLEAR(DimText);
                                  Continue := FALSE;
                                  REPEAT
                                    OldDimText := DimText;
                                    IF DimText = '' THEN
                                      DimText := STRSUBSTNO('%1 %2',DimSetEntry1."Dimension Code",DimSetEntry1."Dimension Value Code")
                                    ELSE
                                      DimText :=
                                        STRSUBSTNO(
                                          '%1, %2 %3',DimText,
                                          DimSetEntry1."Dimension Code",DimSetEntry1."Dimension Value Code");
                                    IF STRLEN(DimText) > MAXSTRLEN(OldDimText) THEN BEGIN
                                      DimText := OldDimText;
                                      Continue := TRUE;
                                      EXIT;
                                    END;
                                  UNTIL DimSetEntry1.NEXT = 0;
                                END;

               DataItemLinkReference=Purchase Header }

    { 71  ;4   ;Column  ;HdrDimCaption       ;
               SourceExpr=HdrDimCaptionLbl }

    { 6547;3   ;DataItem;                    ;
               DataItemTable=Table39;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Document Type,Document No.,Line No.);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               CurrReport.BREAK;
                             END;

               DataItemLinkReference=Purchase Header;
               DataItemLink=Document Type=FIELD(Document Type),
                            Document No.=FIELD(No.) }

    { 7551;3   ;DataItem;RoundLoop           ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               MoreLines := PurchLine.FIND('+');
                               WHILE MoreLines AND (PurchLine.Description = '') AND (PurchLine."Description 2" = '') AND
                                     (PurchLine."No." = '') AND (PurchLine.Quantity = 0) AND
                                     (PurchLine.Amount = 0)
                               DO
                                 MoreLines := PurchLine.NEXT(-1) <> 0;
                               IF NOT MoreLines THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;
                               PurchLine.SETRANGE("Line No.",0,PurchLine."Line No.");
                               SETRANGE(Number,1,PurchLine.COUNT);
                               CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(PurchLine."Line Amount",PurchLine."Inv. Discount Amount");
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  LrecItem@1000 : Record 27;
                                BEGIN
                                  IF Number = 1 THEN
                                    PurchLine.FIND('-')
                                  ELSE
                                    PurchLine.NEXT;

                                  //>> RISA
                                  CLEAR(GcodVendorItemNo);
                                  //<< RISA

                                  //**4PS.sn
                                  IF PurchLine."Trade Item" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                    PurchLine.Type := PurchLine.Type::Item;
                                    PurchLine."No." := PurchLine."Trade Item";
                                    //>> RISA
                                    GcodVendorItemNo := PurchLine."No.";
                                    //<< RISA
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    IF PurchLine."Basic Item" <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                      PurchLine.Type := PurchLine.Type::Item;
                                      PurchLine."No." := PurchLine."Basic Item";
                                      //>> RISA
                                      GcodVendorItemNo := PurchLine."No.";
                                      //<< RISA
                                    END ELSE BEGIN
                                      IF PurchLine."Item No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
                                        PurchLine.Type := PurchLine.Type::Item;
                                        PurchLine."No." := PurchLine."Item No.";
                                        //>> RISA
                                        IF LrecItem.GET(PurchLine."No.") THEN
                                          GcodVendorItemNo := LrecItem."Vendor Item No.";
                                        //<< RISA
                                      END;
                                    END;
                                  END;
                                  //**4PS.en


                                  "Purchase Line" := PurchLine;

                                  IF NOT "Purchase Header"."Prices Including VAT" AND
                                     (PurchLine."VAT Calculation Type" = PurchLine."VAT Calculation Type"::"Full VAT")
                                  THEN
                                    PurchLine."Line Amount" := 0;

                                  IF (PurchLine.Type = PurchLine.Type::"G/L Account") AND (NOT ShowInternalInfo) THEN
                                    "Purchase Line"."No." := '';
                                  AllowInvDisctxt := FORMAT("Purchase Line"."Allow Invoice Disc.");
                                  TotalSubTotal += "Purchase Line"."Line Amount";
                                  TotalInvoiceDiscountAmount -= "Purchase Line"."Inv. Discount Amount";
                                  TotalAmount += "Purchase Line".Amount;
                                END;

               OnPostDataItem=BEGIN
                                PurchLine.DELETEALL;
                              END;
                               }

    { 54  ;4   ;Column  ;LineAmt_PurchLine   ;
               SourceExpr=PurchLine."Line Amount";
               AutoFormatType=1;
               AutoFormatExpr="Purchase Line"."Currency Code" }

    { 226 ;4   ;Column  ;LineNo_PurchLine    ;

               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;

                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1..));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF NOT ShowInternalInfo THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;

                               DimSetEntry2.SETRANGE("Dimension Set ID","Purchase Line"."Dimension Set ID");
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  IF Number = 1 THEN BEGIN
                                    IF NOT DimSetEntry2.FINDSET THEN
                                      CurrReport.BREAK;
                                  END ELSE
                                    IF NOT Continue THEN
                                      CurrReport.BREAK;

                                  CLEAR(DimText);
                                  Continue := FALSE;
                                  REPEAT
                                    OldDimText := DimText;
                                    IF DimText = '' THEN
                                      DimText := STRSUBSTNO('%1 %2',DimSetEntry2."Dimension Code",DimSetEntry2."Dimension Value Code")
                                    ELSE
                                      DimText :=
                                        STRSUBSTNO(
                                          '%1, %2 %3',DimText,
                                          DimSetEntry2."Dimension Code",DimSetEntry2."Dimension Value Code");
                                    IF STRLEN(DimText) > MAXSTRLEN(OldDimText) THEN BEGIN
                                      DimText := OldDimText;
                                      Continue := TRUE;
                                      EXIT;
                                    END;
                                  UNTIL DimSetEntry2.NEXT = 0;
                                END;
                                 }

                               IF (NOT GLSetup."Print VAT specification in LCY") OR

                                 VALSpecLCYHeader := Text007 + Text008
                               ELSE

                               //CurrExchRate.FindCurrency("Purchase Header"."Posting Date","Purchase Header"."Currency Code",1);  //**4PS.o
                               CurrExchRate.FindCurrency(0,'',"Purchase Header"."Posting Date","Purchase Header"."Currency Code",1); //**4PS.n
                               VALExchRate := STRSUBSTNO(Text009,CurrExchRate."Relational Exch. Rate Amount",CurrExchRate."Exchange Rate Amount");
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  VATAmountLine.GetLine(Number);
                                  VALVATBaseLCY :=
                                    VATAmountLine.GetBaseLCY(
                                      "Purchase Header"."Posting Date","Purchase Header"."Currency Code","Purchase Header"."Currency Factor",FALSE);
                                  VALVATAmountLCY :=
                                    VATAmountLine.GetAmountLCY(
                                      "Purchase Header"."Posting Date","Purchase Header"."Currency Code","Purchase Header"."Currency Factor",FALSE);
                                END;
                                 }

  REQUESTPAGE
  {
    PROPERTIES
    {
      SaveValues=Yes;
      OnInit=BEGIN
               LogInteractionEnable := TRUE;

               //**4PS.sn
               ArchiveDocumentEditable := TRUE;
               LogInteractionEditable := TRUE;
               ChangeStatusEditable := TRUE;
               DirectPostOrderEditable := TRUE;
               //**4PS.en
             END;

      OnOpenPage=BEGIN
                   ArchiveDocument := PurchSetup."Archive Quotes and Orders";
                   LogInteraction := SegManagement.FindInteractTmplCode(13) <> '';

                   LogInteractionEnable := LogInteraction;

                   //**4PS.sn
                   DirectPostOrder := DirectPostOrder::"According to Vendor";
                   SampleOrder := FALSE;
                   //**4PS.en
                 END;

    }
    CONTROLS
    {
      { 5   ;0   ;Container ;
                  ContainerType=ContentArea }

      { 3   ;1   ;Group     ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Options }

      { 1   ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=NoofCopies;
                  CaptionML=ENU=No. of Copies;
                  SourceExpr=NoOfCopies }

      { 1100525004;2;Field  ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Sample Order;
                  SourceExpr=SampleOrder;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               //**4PS.sn
                               ArchiveDocumentEditable := NOT SampleOrder;
                               LogInteractionEditable := NOT SampleOrder;
                               ChangeStatusEditable := NOT SampleOrder;
                               DirectPostOrderEditable := NOT SampleOrder;
                               IF SampleOrder THEN BEGIN
                                 ArchiveDocument := FALSE;
                                 LogInteraction := FALSE;
                                 ChangeStatus := ChangeStatus::None;
                                 DirectPostOrder := DirectPostOrder::"According to Vendor";
                               END;
                               //**4PS.en
                             END;
                              }

      { 2   ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=ShowInternalInformation;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Show Internal Information;
                  SourceExpr=ShowInternalInfo }

      { 1100525000;2;Field  ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Print text;
                  SourceExpr=PrintTextBln }

      { 7   ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=ArchiveDocument;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Archive Document;
                  SourceExpr=ArchiveDocument;
                  Editable=ArchiveDocumentEditable;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               IF NOT ArchiveDocument THEN
                                 LogInteraction := FALSE;
                             END;
                              }

      { 4   ;2   ;Field     ;
                  Name=LogInteraction;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Log Interaction;
                  SourceExpr=LogInteraction;
                  Enabled=LogInteractionEnable;
                  Editable=LogInteractionEditable;
                  OnValidate=BEGIN
                               IF LogInteraction THEN
                                 ArchiveDocument := ArchiveDocumentEnable;
                             END;
                              }

      { 1100525001;2;Field  ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Print Blanket Scheme;
                  SourceExpr=PrintBlanketScheme }

      { 1100525002;2;Field  ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Change Status;
                  OptionCaptionML=ENU=None,Released,Closed;
                  SourceExpr=ChangeStatus;
                  Editable=ChangeStatusEditable }

      { 1100525003;2;Field  ;
                  CaptionML=ENU=Direct Post Order;
                  OptionCaptionML=ENU=According to Vendor,Not;
                  SourceExpr=DirectPostOrder;
                  Editable=DirectPostOrderEditable }

    }
  }
  LABELS
  {
  }

      Text000@1000 : TextConst 'ENU=Purchaser';
      Text001@1001 : TextConst 'ENU=Total %1';
      Text002@1002 : TextConst 'ENU=Total %1 Incl. VAT';
      Text003@1003 : TextConst 'ENU=" COPY"';
      Text004@1004 : TextConst 'ENU=PURCHASE ORDER %1';
      Text005@1005 : TextConst 'ENU=Page %1';
      Text006@1006 : TextConst 'ENU=Total %1 Excl. VAT';
      GLSetup@1007 : Record 98;
      CompanyInfo@1008 : Record 79;
      ShipmentMethod@1009 : Record 10;
      PaymentTerms@1010 : Record 3;
      PrepmtPaymentTerms@1064 : Record 3;
      SalesPurchPerson@1011 : Record 13;
      VATAmountLine@1012 : TEMPORARY Record 290;
      PrepmtVATAmountLine@1055 : TEMPORARY Record 290;
      PrePmtVATAmountLineDeduct@1069 : TEMPORARY Record 290;
      PurchLine@1013 : TEMPORARY Record 39;
      DimSetEntry1@1014 : Record 480;
      DimSetEntry2@1015 : Record 480;
      PrepmtDimSetEntry@1057 : Record 480;
      PrepmtInvBuf@1056 : TEMPORARY Record 461;

    PROCEDURE InitializeRequest@4(NewNoOfCopies@1002 : Integer;NewShowInternalInfo@1000 : Boolean;NewArchiveDocument@1001 : Boolean;NewLogInteraction@1003 : Boolean);
    BEGIN
      NoOfCopies := NewNoOfCopies;
      ShowInternalInfo := NewShowInternalInfo;
      ArchiveDocument := NewArchiveDocument;
      LogInteraction := NewLogInteraction;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CheckPrintBlanketScheme@1210190007();
    VAR
      PurchaseHeader@1210190001 : Record 38;
      DocumentPrint@1210190002 : Codeunit 229;
    BEGIN
      //**4PS.n
      IF NOT PrintBlanketScheme THEN
        EXIT;

      PurchaseHeader.COPYFILTERS("Purchase Header");
      PurchaseHeader.SETRANGE("Purchase Order Type", PurchaseHeader."Purchase Order Type"::"Blanket Order");
      PurchaseHeader.SETRANGE("Blanket Scheme", TRUE);
      IF NOT PurchaseHeader.FINDFIRST THEN
        EXIT;

      //PurchaseHeader.SETRANGE("Purchase Order Type");  //* These filters are already set in the report,
      //PurchaseHeader.SETRANGE("Blanket Scheme");       //* you do not want them as selection fields
      DocumentPrint.PrintBlanketScheme(PurchaseHeader);
    END;

    PROCEDURE CheckDimensionAddress@1100485005(Dim1Code@1100485003 : Code[20]);
    VAR
      Contact@1100485002 : Record 5050;
      DimensionValue@1100485001 : Record 349;
      DimensionManagement@1100485000 : Codeunit 408;
    BEGIN
      //**4PS
      IF Dim1Code <> '' THEN BEGIN
        DimensionManagement.GetDimValueRec(1, Dim1Code, DimensionValue, TRUE, '');
        IF DimensionValue."Contact No. (Company)" <> '' THEN BEGIN
          Contact.GET(DimensionValue."Contact No. (Company)");
          FormatAddr.ContactAddr(CompanyAddr, Contact);
        END;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CheckPhase@1100409000();
    VAR
      PhasePlanMgt@1100409002 : Codeunit 11012242;
      PlanAction@1100409001 : 'Consent,Print,ICMStatus,Word,Confirm,OrderStatus,QuoteStatus,Manual,E-mail,GS1';
      PurchasePlanPhase@1100409000 : Record 11020417;
    BEGIN
      //**4PS
      PhasePlanMgt.TestPhaseCanBeFinished("Purchase Header", PlanAction::Print, 1, PurchasePlanPhase);  //db, 25-04-13: C005395
    END;

    PROCEDURE FillJobInfo@1100525002();
    VAR
      PurchaseLine@1100525000 : Record 39;
    BEGIN
      //**4PS
      JobNoLabelTxt := '';
      JobNoTxt := '';

      IF "Purchase Header"."Job No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
        JobNoLabelTxt := "Purchase Header".FIELDCAPTION("Job No.");
        JobNoTxt := "Purchase Header"."Job No.";
      END ELSE IF "Purchase Header"."Service Order No." <> '' THEN BEGIN
        JobNoLabelTxt := "Purchase Header".FIELDCAPTION("Service Order No.");
        JobNoTxt := "Purchase Header"."Service Order No.";
      END ELSE BEGIN
        PurchaseLine.SETRANGE("Document Type", "Purchase Header"."Document Type");
        PurchaseLine.SETRANGE("Document No.", "Purchase Header"."No.");
        PurchaseLine.SETFILTER(Type, '<>%1', PurchaseLine.Type::" ");
        PurchaseLine.SETFILTER("Job No.", '<>%1', '');
        IF PurchaseLine.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          JobNoLabelTxt := "Purchase Header".FIELDCAPTION("Job No.");
          JobNoTxt := PurchaseLine."Job No.";
        END ELSE BEGIN
          PurchaseLine.SETRANGE("Document Type", "Purchase Header"."Document Type");
          PurchaseLine.SETRANGE("Document No.", "Purchase Header"."No.");
          PurchaseLine.SETFILTER(Type, '<>%1', PurchaseLine.Type::" ");
          PurchaseLine.SETFILTER("Service Order No.", '<>%1', '');
          IF PurchaseLine.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
            JobNoLabelTxt := "Purchase Header".FIELDCAPTION("Service Order No.");
            JobNoTxt := PurchaseLine."Service Order No.";
          END;
        END;
      END;
    END;

    LOCAL PROCEDURE LfncGetTextLines@41(PintTextNo@1000 : Integer;PcodLanguage@1001 : Code[10];PoptType@1002 : 'HeaderText,FooterText,FooterNote') LtxtTextLine : Text;
    VAR
      LrecAddText@1003 : Record 50005;
    BEGIN
      //>> RISA
      LrecAddText.SETRANGE(Company,COMPANYNAME);
      LrecAddText.SETRANGE("Document Type",LrecAddText."Document Type"::PurchaseOrder);
      LrecAddText.SETRANGE(Type,PoptType);
      LrecAddText.SETRANGE("Language Code",PcodLanguage);
      IF NOT LrecAddText.ISEMPTY THEN BEGIN
        IF LrecAddText.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
          CASE PintTextNo OF
            1: LtxtTextLine := LrecAddText."Text 1";
            2: LtxtTextLine := LrecAddText."Text 2";
            3: LtxtTextLine := LrecAddText."Text 3";
            4: LtxtTextLine := LrecAddText."Text 4";
          END;
        END;
      END;
      //<< RISA
    END;

    BEGIN
    {
      Developer Date       Description
      ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      RISA      19-12-2014 Object created
      RISA      02-01-2015 Transport footer added, purchaser added
    }
    END.
  }

      </Page>

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Shared offset as Integer
Shared newPage as Object
Shared currentgroup1 as Object
Shared currentgroup2 as Object
Shared currentgroup3 as Object
Public Function GetGroupPageNumber(NewPage as Boolean, pagenumber as Integer) as Object
  If NewPage
    offset = pagenumber - 1
  End If
  Return pagenumber - offset
End Function

Public Function IsNewPage(group1 as Object, group2 as Object, group3 as Object) As Boolean
newPage = FALSE
If Not (group1 = currentgroup1)
    newPage = TRUE
    currentgroup1 = group1
    currentgroup2 = group2
    currentgroup3 = group3
     ELSE 
      If Not (group2 = currentgroup2)
        newPage = TRUE 
        currentgroup2 = group2
        currentgroup3 = group3
        ELSE
          If Not (group3 = currentgroup3)
          newPage = TRUE 
          currentgroup3 = group3
         End If
     End If
  End If
Return newPage
End Function

Shared Data1 as Object

Public Function GetData(Num as Integer, Group as integer) as Object
if Group = 1 then
   Return Cstr(Choose(Num, Split(Cstr(Data1),Chr(177))))
End If
End Function

Public Function SetData(NewData as Object,Group as integer)
  If Group = 1 and NewData &lt;&gt; "" Then
      Data1 = NewData
  End If
End Function

Shared TotalPage as Integer
Public Function SetTotalPage(Value as Integer)
        TotalPage = Value
End Function

Public Function GetTotalPage()as Integer
        Return TotalPage
End Function

Shared NewData as Object
Shared Function SetNewData(Value as Object)
        NewData = Value
End Function

Shared Function GetNewData() as Object
        Return NewData
End Function

Shared ReportTotal As Double = 0

Public Function SetReportTotal(ByVal val As Double) As Double
       ReportTotal = val
       Return val
End Function

Public Function GetReportTotal() As Double
       Return ReportTotal
End Function</Code>
